    "date": "2023-09-01T14:04:16Z",
    "text": "Communications, Video, and Technology Accessibility Act of 2022\n\nThis bill expands, and establishes new, requirements to increase the accessibility of communications technologies for individuals who are blind or deaf or have other disabilities, including by requiring closed captioning for online video programming and audio descriptions for both online and televised video programming."
